Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠…好喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  早上好  奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这身衣服很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小悠你不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉你好像在想心事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是认真地在想  奈绪会穿怎样可爱的衣服来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒好
